r />\n<br />\n愛之深, 責之切,<br />\n<br />\n不論香港的結局如何, 大家都是同舟人, 目標一致, 即使方法不同亦永不割席! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"講得如此有道理，請他走上前線帶領"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"唔係個個行動上出到嚟, 認同既可以幫手spread開<br />\n玩火我其實唔反對, 有需要時就要去做<br />\n但唔好亂咁玩<br />\n例如琴晚cwb我就覺得冇必要<br />\n始終汽油彈扔葵涌警署, 我覺得某程度上算係對準政權, 但係呢一著岩同錯我真係答唔到你住, 要d時間思考<br />\n最後就係盡量提醒各位be humble<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明有d人仲係和理非時被差佬無理執法/暴力對待過, 仇警心態一定有, 我都有. 有時控制唔到情緒明白既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但記住目標&gt;仇恨"},{"pid":"e12de57b5c693945d539d336500372317155cb0e","tid":1417038,"uid":299775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de6ad3c2edf4026602feb84679a2438ada9c8d5b","tid":1417038,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"和理非時間 俾啲豬抖抖氣先"},{"pid":"63bf9da7acde704093763a58d4c69333f6acb49a","tid":1417038,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8f9b51f8693cd204328246e423200826b98e6c","tid":1417038,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"（和理非升級）下一步：罷消費、罷交稅！不設期限！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候和理非了"},{"pid":"287cb89926599c5a9e9e3b7d6173f0684039d6c2","tid":1417038,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53452f209be11b65a593347e8f2f4415ef03150","tid":1417038,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p